photo.alt: A picture of four hands holding eachother over a restaurant table. Each hand belongs to a different girl. I'm wearing fingerless fishnet gloves and purple nail polish. The girl to the right of me is wearing black nail polish and a ring, and has a glass with some red drink. The girl opposite of me is holding a drink in her other hand (also with black nail polish) and has her phone in front of her on the table with a rainbow flag sticker on it. The girl next to her is the only one not wearing nail polish. It's all very cute.
